## How to contribute new decisions
- Firm premise: append to "#N" section, sequential numbering
- ADR: append to end of "ADRs" section, ADR-NNN sequential numbering
- Chronological history lives in `git log`, not here — this doc is current state
- Optional `**Status**:` / `**Tags**:` lines on any entry are recognised by
  the `rsct_get_decisions` tool's `filter.status` / `filter.tag` arguments.
  Status values: `active`, `superseded`, `deprecated`. Tags are
  comma-separated free-form strings.
